Date: Thu, 26 Mar 2026 03:07:55 +0700
Subject: [PATCH] test sus 11

---
 kernel/Kbuild            |  10 +++
 kernel/Kconfig           |  89 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 kernel/kernel_umount.c   |  13 +++-
 kernel/kernel_umount.h   |   2 +
 kernel/ksu.c             |  11 ++++
 kernel/ksud.c            |  48 +++++++-------
 kernel/selinux/rules.c   |   6 ++
 kernel/selinux/selinux.c |  96 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 kernel/selinux/selinux.h |  13 ++++
